article.description: — Sean Conway had 28 points in VMI's 80-72 victory over Navy on Saturday.
article.headline: Conway's 28 points help VMI take down Navy 80-72
article.linkText: Conway's 28 points help VMI take down Navy 80-72
article.story: LEXINGTON, Va. -- — Sean Conway had 28 points in VMI's 80-72 victory over Navy on Saturday. Conway also had five rebounds for the Keydets (3-6). Tyler Houser added 16 points while shooting 6 for 9, including 4 for 5 from beyond the arc, and they also had eight rebounds. Devin Butler shot 5 for 10, including 3 for 6 from beyond the arc to finish with 13 points. The Midshipmen (5-3) were led by Austin Inge, who posted 21 points. Tyler Nelson added 15 points, six rebounds and three blocks for Navy. Patrick Dorsey also had 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
